Text:
Pokemon Black works great on my R4DS card! And it's in fully English.

No save errors or something. But needed to update. (http://www.r4wood.com/Kernel/h/Wood_R4_v1.26.rar) 
1.Download latest version.
2.Unrar it.
3.Copy DS_Menu_DAT & _Rpg to Map and Overwrite it
4. Done

Don't know if white works but think it would.

@Koedje, Get version 1.26 See link above.

@Remember 1234, Make sure you have the right version that's compatible with your card. Mine froze and got an error to without the update.

@Dungermum, It's an UK/Euro Rom
